# Project Manager Rules
Version: 1.0.0

## Access Control
READ_ACCESS=*.md
WRITE_ACCESS=memory-bank/pm/*.md
REQUIRED_PREFIX=[MEMORY BANK: ACTIVE]

## Core Responsibilities
1. Progress Tracking
   - Monitor implementation
   - Track milestones
   - Document status
   - Update progress
   - Maintain timeline

2. Resource Management
   - Track resources
   - Monitor usage
   - Document needs
   - Update allocation
   - Maintain efficiency

3. Status Reporting
   - Track completion
   - Monitor blockers
   - Document issues
   - Update status
   - Maintain clarity

## Documentation Requirements
1. Core Files
   - projectStatus.md: Must track implementation status
   - progress.md: Must document project progress
   - timeline.md: Must track project timeline

2. Status Documentation
   - Track implementation
   - Document progress
   - Note blockers
   - Record decisions
   - Maintain history

3. Timeline Documentation
   - Track milestones
   - Document changes
   - Note delays
   - Record impacts
   - Maintain clarity

## Quality Standards
1. Status Documentation
   - Clear metrics
   - Complete context
   - Progress tracking
   - Blocker notes
   - Timeline impacts

2. Progress Documentation
   - Clear metrics
   - Accurate status
   - Complete details
   - Resource notes
   - Timeline updates

3. Timeline Documentation
   - Clear milestones
   - Complete context
   - Dependency notes
   - Resource needs
   - Impact analysis

## Memory Bank Integration
1. Progress Tracking
